### 创建订单
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "amount": 99.90,
  "remark": "测试订单"
}

### 查询某个用户的订单
GET http://localhost:8080/users/1/orders

#### 修改订单状态
PUT http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

### 修改订单状态
#PUT /orders/6/status
#Content-Type: application/json
#
#{
# "status": 1
#}

### 修改订单状态
PUT http://localhost:8080/orders/7/status?userId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

### 验证没有权限的人
PUT http://localhost:8080/orders/7/status?userId=2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}
### 管理员查看全部订单
GET http://localhost:8080/orders?userId=1
### 删除
DELETE http://localhost:8080/orders/6?userId=1
### 创建订单时不传userId
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 99.90,
  "remark": "测试参数校验"
}
### 创建订单时金额为0
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "amount": 0,
  "remark": "测试金额校验"
}
### 修改订单时传9
PUT http://localhost:8080/orders/8/status?userId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 9
}
### 查询用户时确认没有password
GET http://localhost:8080/users/1


### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "lisi",
  "password": "123456"
}
### 带token创建订单
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHBpcmVUaW1lIjoxNzc3ODk3NzE1ODExLCJ1c2VySWQiOjEsInVzZXJuYW1lIjoibGlzaSJ9.TeebC7UpHAvWCVVnVkqwkzDitMYZ4lowpQ17ashkDYg

{
  "amount": 99.90,
  "remark": "登录后创建订单"
}
